author: Milford Mirror
title: Girls volleyball: Law falls to Tigers in five
text:
Jonathan Law forced a fifth set before losing a 3-2 decision to visiting Daniel Hand from Madison on Monday. 
Hand improved to 10-6 with the 22-25, 25-19, 25-20, 18-25, 15-8 win. Law is 6-12. 
Kailee Frank had 15 kills, Kristin Frank 22 assists and Victoria Contaxis 14 digs for Law. 
Hand’s Krissy LaSance had 13 digs, Ryann Corniello 13 kills and Olive Finke 14 digs. Related posts:
